search_results.title: David Jasper
search_results.snippet: David Jasper (born 1 August 1951) is a professor emeritus of Literature and Theology at the University of Glasgow. Contents.

search_results.title: James M. Jasper
search_results.snippet: James Macdonald Jasper (born 1957) is a writer and sociologist who has taught Ph.D. students at the Graduate Center of the City University of New York

search_results.title: Welcome to the Jasper Fforde Website - Overview page
search_results.snippet: Welcome to the jasper Fforde website, and yes, Jasper Fforde is my real name. I am a British writer who lives in Wales and writes absurdist fiction.
